(1, 'If you start counting at one and spell out the numbers as you go, you won''t use the letter ', 'Do You know ', 'If you start counting at one and spell out the numbers as you go, you won''t use the letter "A" until you reach 1,000', '1389161137l.jpg', 1),
(2, '12+1 = 11+2, and &quot;twelve plus one&quot; is an anagram of &quot;eleven plus two. &quot;', 'Do You Know ?', '12+1 = 11+2, and &quot;twelve plus one&quot; is an anagram of &quot;eleven plus two. &quot;', '1389183526.jpg', 1),
