(2, 'DESIGN OF AN ANIMATED ELECTRONIC BOOK', 'COMPUTER MATHEMATICS', 'FUT MINNA', 'DESIGN OF AN ANIMATED ELECTRONIC BOOK\r\n(Case study: Motions in Physics)\r\n\r\n\r\nby\r\n\r\nEHIWE, McDonald\r\n2006/25460BM\r\n\r\n\r\nProject Submitted to the Department of Mathematics and Computer Science\r\n Federal ', 'ABSTRACT\r\nMultimedia is being used increasingly to provide computer based instruction. One reason for this trend is the assumption that multimedia information helps people learn. To find out whether t', 'TABLE OF CONTENTS\r\nContent												Pages\r\nTitle Page												i\r\nDeclaration												ii\r\nCertification												iii\r\nDedication												iv\r\nAcknowledgement											v\r\nAbstract										', 1, '0000-00-00'),
(4, 'DESIGN OF AN ANIMATED ELECTRONIC BOOK', 'Mathematics and Computer Science', 'Federal University of Technology ', '<h2>DESIGN OF AN ANIMATED ELECTRONIC BOOK</h2><br/><br/><h4>(Case study: Motions in Physics)</h4><br/><br/><br/>', '<I>Multimedia is being used increasingly to provide computer based instruction. One reason for this trend is the assumption that multimedia information helps people learn. To find out whether there is empirical support for this assumption, this project reviews studies from a wide variety of fields to show that multimedia -may be able to help people learn more information more quickly compared to traditional classroom lecture. It also goes a long way to establish the fact that an average student or individualâ€™s creativity is enhanced through the use of multimedia in learning</I>', '<table width="100%" border="0">\r\n  <tr>\r\n    <td><center>Content</center></td>\r\n    <td><center>pages</center></td>\r\n  </tr>\r\n  <tr>\r\n    <td>Title Page</td>\r\n    <td>i</td>\r\n  </tr>\r\n  <tr>\r\n    <td>Declaration</td>\r\n    <td>ii</td>\r\n  </tr>\r\n    <tr>\r\n    <td>Certification</td>\r\n    <td>iii</td>\r\n  </tr>  <tr>\r\n    <td>Dedication</td>\r\n    <td>iv</td>\r\n  </tr>  <tr>\r\n    <td>Acknowledgement</td>\r\n    <td>v</td>\r\n  </tr>\r\n   <tr>\r\n    <td>Abstract</td>\r\n    <td>vi</td>\r\n  </tr> <tr>\r\n    <td>Table of contents</td>\r\n    <td>vii</td>\r\n  </tr> <tr>\r\n    <td>List of Tables </td>\r\n    <td>xi</td>\r\n  </tr>\r\n  <tr>\r\n    <td>List of figures</td>\r\n    <td>xii</td>\r\n  </tr>\r\n</table>', 1, '0000-00-00');

